            <div class="menu__item-intro">
              <h2 class="menu__item-intro-title">Where we work</h2>
                              <div class="menu__item-intro-text">
                  <p>We work in 123 countries and territories, combining emergency assistance with long-term development while adapting our activities to the context and challenges of each location and its people.</p>

